node.text: This might be the best shower of my life. Honestly, water efficient AND powerful - is there a better combination? The Nebia by Moen Quattro by @nebiainc is true luxury and each mode saves 40-50% of water. Check them out (they just launched on Kickstarter, link in Stories) and do good for your body and the planet. #ad #NebiaShower

node.text: We adopted “Kitty” through our amazing veterinarian @theswiftiekittens ! Jessica raised Kitty until we were able to adopt her. Since she does monthly check up on all of the animals, Jessica will be able to watch Kitty grow up! I hope everyone has a beautiful day and week!!! Don’t forget, consistency defines who we are, not our mistakes. Every day we all have a choice to start our days with intentions. Eventually those intentions become our gifts to the world. The energy we all breath and spread to each other. I love you all and thanks for being a part of this beautiful journey with me. Sending you love, light and laughter ❤️❤️🐾 oh and yea, I definitely had donkey poop on my pants, a lot of it.... anyways, welcome to the family Kitty and thanks so much @theswiftiekittens !

node.text: She was afraid of me because she needed me. That’s what I told myself when I saw her. As It’s always the ones that fear love the most that need it the most. And eventually, they give it the most. I’m not a bit surprised about the bond Ella and I have together, I knew we would the second I met her. She’s too much for many but perfect for me. What a blessing we are for each other, what a life as it was meant to be. ❤️🐾🐾#AdoptDontShop

node.text: Every day is dog day around here. And also a good boondoggle if we’re being honest, which is why we’re so excited to partner with @lagunitasbeer to celebrate our best furry friends for International Dog Day. Lagunitas has supported dog rescues for decades - and did you know that there is a dog featured on every bottle or can? Real deal. Check out the link in my bio to learn more about how you can enter to win a Lagunitas sponsored boondoggle for you and your pups this summer.  #LagunitasDogContest #LagunitasBrewing #BeerSpeaksDogsDrool #Ad21+ #PaidInBeer
